              "openLinksInNewTab": true,
              "markdown": "# Welcome to the Multi-Panel Showcase\nThis dashboard demonstrates all supported panel types in the kb-yaml-to-lens compiler:\n- **Markdown panels** - Rich text content with formatting\n- **Links panels** - Navigation to dashboards and external URLs\n- **Chart panels** - Multiple visualization types (Metric, Pie, Line, Bar, Area, Tagcloud)\n_Note: Image panels are defined in the schema but compilation is not yet implemented._\nUse this as a reference for building your own dashboards!\n"
